high_descs: Turn left and walk to the counter, then take a left and walk straight to the other counter.
Pick up the ladle on the counter.
Turn right and walk to the sink.
Rinse the ladle in the sink.
Turn left and walk back to the counter.
Place the ladle on the counter to the right of the spoon.
anns.task_desc: Place a rinsed ladle on a counter.

high_descs: Turn left for six steps, turn left and walk straight to the far counter.
Pick up the ladle with the blue handle.
Turn around and take three steps and turn left to face the sink.

Put the ladle in the sink with the handle straight up and the spoon side at the bottom right corner of the sponge; turn on the water and rinse for a couple seconds, turn off the water and pick up the ladle.
Turn left and walk straight to the counter.
Set the ladle on the counter, centering it between the bucket and the silver spoon, with the handle facing the wall.
anns.task_desc: Put a rinsed ladle on the counter.

high_descs: Turn left and walk over to the counter, then hang a left and walk up to the counter.
Pick up the large golden spoon off of the counter.
Turn around and walk forward, then turn left to face the sink.
Wash the large golden spoon in the sink and then pick it back up.
Turn left and walk over to the counter.
Put the clean golden spoon on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean golden spoon on the counter.
